{"items":{"4":{"ordinal":3,"content":"<p>Functions to export<\/p><ul><li>showCreateProjectDialog<\/li><li>showProjectPropertiesDialog<\/li><\/ul>","type":"idea","treeType":"horizontal","parent":"root"},"1":{"ordinal":1,"content":"<p>Code generation<\/p><ul><li>Do not add any dependencies to the module.<\/li><li>Do not use \"class\", \"new\", and \"this\" keywords.<\/li><li>Do not use object destructuring.<\/li><li>Add async\/await where necessary.<\/li><li>Use \"undefined\" instead of \"null\".<\/li><li>Do not use array.length = 0 trick.<\/li><li>Use plain JS objects for dictionaries and sets.<\/li><li>Use {} to create new dictionaries and sets.<\/li><li>Use \"in\" operator to check if a key is in the map or set.<\/li><li>Keep snake case identifier style where the specs follow it.<\/li><li>Add async marker where necessary.<\/li><li>Report the errors instead of generating code if there are critical errors.<\/li><\/ul>","type":"idea","treeType":"horizontal","parent":"root"},"5":{"ordinal":5,"content":"<p>Module global variables:<\/p><ul><li>globalOptions<\/li><\/ul>","type":"idea","treeType":"horizontal","parent":"root"},"2":{"ordinal":0,"content":"<p>Properties<\/p><ul><li>format: IIFE<\/li><li>language: JavaScript<\/li><li>target: browser<\/li><\/ul>","type":"idea","treeType":"horizontal","parent":"root"},"6":{"ordinal":4,"content":"<p>Generate clear, setValue, and addEventListener<\/p>","type":"idea","parent":"root","treeType":"horizontal"},"root":{"type":"header","treeType":"horizontal"},"3":{"ordinal":2,"content":"<p>How to export function foo:<\/p><p>    window.foo = foo<\/p>","type":"idea","treeType":"horizontal","parent":"root"}},"type":"graf"}